{"tid":1599153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一唔理其他區，後果可以好嚴重！","createTime":"2019-09-27T22:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T22:59:57.000Z","uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"463c13cb475c7b2d6850d91b23211b132e626a45","tid":1599153,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T22:09:16.000Z","msg":"其他區無人理，就等於白白送畀一眾愛國團體搞國慶活動，夾埋紅媒做 show<br />\n<br />\n愛國團體會由得你班人係港島塞住，其他區佢地霸曬，一遍歌舞昇平，然後全日就咁過左，到入夜先返返其他區已經太遲，make noice 既黃金時間已過<br />\n<br />\n大家如果覺得應該由得愛國團體做 show，唔干擾既，可以參加民陣既遊行，民陣十一遊行獲批不反對通知書既機率係 99%<br />\n<br />\n但記住，我地口號係「光復香港」而非「光復港島」<br />\n<br />\n睇完都決定去港島既（如果你唔係住港島），我只能奉勸一句：黑警如果咁好死會批不反對通知書，你就知道件事唔簡單，希望你地理性思考，以大局為重"},{"pid":"95b6485cc63a1cd9b468d775c9b1abbfd0d1c515","tid":1599153,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T22:09:27.000Z","msg":"民陣十一遊行獲批不反對通知書既機率係 99%"},{"pid":"7345b05bb0ea757de4f92a35eb63395138534e31","tid":1599153,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T22:16:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2